according to Rudolf Clausius,

00:04:45.813 --> 00:04:47.253
and I'm gonna paraphrase this,

00:04:47.253 --> 00:04:49.157
is that we don't see spontaneous,

00:04:49.157 --> 00:04:50.515
let me write this down.

