He said, we don't see
a spontaneous transfer

00:05:02.560 --> 00:05:06.519
of heat from cold areas to hot areas.

00:05:06.519 --> 00:05:09.155
So Second Law of Thermodynamics.

00:05:09.155 --> 00:05:13.380
So no transfer, no spontaneous.

00:05:13.392 --> 00:05:15.761
We can use work,

00:05:15.761 --> 00:05:17.693
like things like refrigeration equipment

00:05:17.693 --> 00:05:21.717
to make heat flow

00:05:21.717 --> 00:05:24.190
from cold to hot and cool something down.

00:05:24.190 --> 00:05:26.971
But no spontaneous transfer,

00:05:27.220 --> 00:05:30.256
transfer of heat,

00:05:31.922 --> 00:05:36.922
from cold to hot.

00:05:38.099 --> 00:05:40.455
And maybe I'll underline hot

