I'm not talking about
just three molecules,

00:07:20.417 --> 00:07:21.961
I'm talking about

00:07:21.961 --> 00:07:24.690
way, way more than three molecules

00:07:24.690 --> 00:07:27.865
that you're just never
going to actually see it.

