And you can think about this,

00:07:29.461 --> 00:07:32.637
if we were to allow
ourselves to look at the

00:07:33.060 --> 00:07:34.419
molecular level of things.

00:07:34.419 --> 00:07:36.184
To not just look at the macro level.

00:07:36.184 --> 00:07:37.943
You could see why this is.

