Let me draw a container here.

00:07:45.657 --> 00:07:47.533
If you were to have a container.

00:07:48.119 --> 00:07:51.393
And you have, on the left-hand side,

00:07:51.393 --> 00:07:54.766
lets say you start with a bunch
of molecules that are hot.

00:07:54.980 --> 00:07:57.076
So they have a high kinetic energy.

00:07:57.558 --> 00:07:59.787
So these are, these have

