But on average, the have
a lower kinetic energy.

00:08:24.992 --> 00:08:28.823
So we see that the, we see,

00:08:28.823 --> 00:08:30.983
that the temperature here is lower.

00:08:30.983 --> 00:08:32.336
So let me write this down.

00:08:32.457 --> 00:08:33.723
Right now where we're starting off,

00:08:33.723 --> 00:08:36.840
this has a lower temperature.

00:08:37.055 --> 00:08:39.992
While the left-hand side
has a higher temperature.

00:08:39.992 --> 00:08:41.490
Now what's going to happen?

00:08:41.490 --> 00:08:43.591
These molecules, they can
interact with each other.

00:08:43.591 --> 00:08:45.054
